00:33.149 --> 00:34.779
My next guest is a Bombay lady

00:34.979 --> 00:36.979
Who's following is growing around the world.

00:36.979 --> 00:43.679
She says that you have the power to deal positively with every problem from common to cancer.

00:43.679 --> 00:46.879
All you have to do is now have a tap... , tapping that power.

00:46.969 --> 00:51.279
Please welcome the lady acclaimed as India's greatest living Saint,

00:51.279 --> 00:59.319
the Mother of Sahaja Yoga, Shri Mataji.
Welcome.

00:59.319 --> 01:04.379
I know it's ...Welcome to Australia, I know it's very difficult for you, for anyone to sum up one's religion,

01:04.379 --> 01:08.279
but is it possible to say what is Sahaja Yoga?

01:08.279 --> 01:13.079
Sahaja- "saha" means "with"," ja" is "born with you".

01:13.079 --> 01:16.279
This is born with you. Within us is the power

01:16.779 --> 01:20.779
which can give us the status of a Spirit.

01:20.779 --> 01:22.509
We are not yet the Spirit.

01:22.509 --> 01:25.279
We are at a human level .

01:25.279 --> 01:32.279
And in the evolutionary process we have to now have the breakthrough to become the Spirit.

01:32.279 --> 01:34.369
That's very essential and is absolutely

01:34.369 --> 01:40.279
eventually the all possible natural thing that has to happen.

01:40.359 --> 01:47.479
It should happen to all of us and the time has come for you to get to that position where you become the Spirit.

01:47.479 --> 01:54.479
All the religions have talked about it and told about it, but people have gone wrong in believing that

01:54.489 --> 01:59.479
artificially if you say that you are baptized

01:59.479 --> 02:04.779
or you have become a Brahmin or you have become a pire that you have become the Spirit.

02:04.779 --> 02:08.379
It's not that.
It's a happening that has to take place within ourselves

02:08.409 --> 02:15.679
Which is a living process, absolutely a living process of living Divine force within ourselves.

02:15.699 --> 02:19.479
How does this.. we have heard of lots of yogas,

02:19.569 --> 02:23.489
How does this differ from other any yoga?

02:23.489 --> 02:28.579
Other yoga's were practiced mostly after getting Realization.

02:28.619 --> 02:33.679
But as it has come from some half-baked people,

02:33.689 --> 02:39.079
it is in a very funny way that people follow it as if they have to take all the medicines together.

02:39.079 --> 02:42.079
And they don't know any discrimination about it.

02:42.129 --> 02:47.279
Unless and until you make this force rise within you, you will not know

02:47.279 --> 02:51.279
what type of attention is needed

02:51.379 --> 02:54.579
and what type of physical exercise is needed.

02:54.639 --> 02:58.079
Indiscriminately people do physical exercises getting into trouble.

02:58.079 --> 03:03.079
Now you are speaking of the force. Is it possible to say where this force emanate from?

03:03.079 --> 03:09.279
This force is a residual power in our triangular bone called as sacrum.

03:09.979 --> 03:11.729
Sacrum

03:11.729 --> 03:15.079
Now the sacrum is a word that comes from Greece

03:15.079 --> 03:19.659
and that means Greek people knew this was a sacred bone.

03:19.659 --> 03:23.849
It rises from there, passes through our six centers

03:23.849 --> 03:31.479
piercing through our fontanel bone area and you get the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost coming out of your head.

03:31.479 --> 03:35.279
-That's what Christians refer to it?
- Yes. I mean, Holy Ghost.

03:35.279 --> 03:38.079
What is the Holy Ghost? Nobody can explain,

03:38.079 --> 03:43.079
but Holy Ghost is very simple to understand. This is the reflection of the Holy Ghost within us.

03:43.089 --> 03:46.079
Holy Ghost is the desire of God.

03:46.149 --> 03:50.279
God Himself watches the working of the desire.

03:50.279 --> 03:56.279
And the desire is that we all should become the Spirit.

03:56.279 --> 04:03.479
And this desire is reflected in our triangular bone, in three and a half coils. When it..

04:03.479 --> 04:07.579
-Is this the central nervous system?
-No. It is in the triangular bone.

04:07.579 --> 04:10.579
It's this force. This is the forth force within us. You see,

04:10.579 --> 04:13.679
we have sympathetic nervous system, left and right

04:13.679 --> 04:17.879
and we have got autonomous, that is an autonomous nervous system and parasympathetic

04:17.879 --> 04:19.879
and we have also central nervous system.

04:19.879 --> 04:22.979
Now this is the system which is not yet working.

04:22.979 --> 04:25.279
It is still in the triangular bone.

04:25.359 --> 04:30.279
When it rises it gives you you a new dimension of the Spirit.

04:30.279 --> 04:34.679
Means the light of the Spirit comes in our attention.

04:34.679 --> 04:38.919
In that case what happens. It's very simple to understand that

04:39.279 --> 04:44.379
at human level we are not in the absolute state,

04:44.379 --> 04:47.279
not in the absolute state. That's why there is a chaos.

04:47.279 --> 04:50.579
Supposing I'm holding a snake in my hands, you see, and there's no light.

04:50.579 --> 04:53.779
Somebody tells me that there's a snake. I will not throw it away.

04:53.779 --> 04:56.779
I would not like to listen to anybody's advice about it.

04:56.779 --> 04:58.779
But if there's a light, I'll throw it away.

04:58.779 --> 05:04.379
In the same way when you become the Spirit, the light of the Spirit guides you.

05:04.389 --> 05:09.679
You become your own master, you become your own guru. You don't have to have any guru for that.

05:09.759 --> 05:14.779
This piercing of the fontanel bone by the Kundalini

05:14.779 --> 05:17.079
gives you the power of the Spirit.

05:17.079 --> 05:20.979
