05:25.079 --> 05:26.779
-No, it's an energy.
-An energy, alright.

05:26.779 --> 05:31.579
It's an energy, which comes out of your fontanel bone area, here,

05:31.579 --> 05:35.879
area, touching the Spirit,
but the Spirit actually resides in the heart.

05:35.919 --> 05:40.579
